        public static Map<String,double[]> getTotalGrades(int[] hwIds,
                                                  String studentId)
                                           throws DBException
        Gets the total of the modified grades of one student on each assignment. Called by GradeSet() constructor.

        hwIds - the ID numbers of the assignments
        studentId - login ID of student whose results to get, or null to get grades of all students in the course
